flowchart TD
    A[Heap / Index 中的真实数据] --> B[ANALYZE 抽样]
    B --> C[pg_class: reltuples / relpages]
    B --> D[pg_statistic / pg_stats]
    B --> E[pg_statistic_ext_data / pg_stats_ext]

    C --> F[基础行数与页数]
    D --> G[单列选择率]
    E --> H[同表多列联合选择率]

    F --> I[节点基数估算]
    G --> I
    H --> I

    I --> J[成本比较与 Join 顺序]
    J --> K{执行方式}
    K -->|Literal| L[常量可见]
    K -->|Custom Plan| M[本次参数可见]
    K -->|Generic Plan| N[参数不可见]

    L --> O[执行器]
    M --> O
    N --> O

    O --> P[实际 rows / loops / buffers / temp / WAL]
    P --> Q{估算是否失真}
    Q -->|否| R[保持策略并持续监控]
    Q -->|是| S[定位最早误差]
    S --> T[ANALYZE / 提高列级目标]
    S --> U[CREATE STATISTICS]
    S --> V[索引或 SQL 重构]
    S --> W[Custom/Generic/pgx 模式调整]
